---
name: Web Search Citations Test
description: Prompt crafted to elicit citations via native web_search annotations
version: 1.0.0

inputs:
  topic:
    description: Time-sensitive topic to force web search
    type: string
    default: "NVDA closing price yesterday site:nasdaq.com OR site:finance.yahoo.com OR site:investors.nvidia.com"

model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    connection: openai_conn
    model: gpt-5-mini
    type: openai_chat
    tools: [web_search]
  parameters:
    max_tokens: 250
    include:
      - "web_search_call.results"

processing_config:
  source_collection: Domain

---

system:
You are a web search testing assistant. Your ONLY job is to use the native web_search tool for the given query and answer briefly based on what you find.

Requirements:
- ALWAYS use web_search first
- Keep the answer short (one or two sentences)
- You may include URLs inline if helpful (not required)

user:
Find the answer to: "{{ topic }}" and respond briefly.
